sequenceDiagram
  participant OP as Operator
  participant UI as Dispatch.svelte
  participant BE as webshell binary
  participant LSQ as lightsquad
  participant RT as Runner trait
  participant PROV as Provider
  participant AYIN as AYIN
  OP->>UI: Click provider pill
  UI->>UI: Open drawer (provider-select)
  OP->>UI: Save anthropic-http + model
  UI->>BE: POST /api/copilot/provider {base_url, model, api_key}
  BE->>BE: SSRF guard + keychain store
  BE-->>UI: 200 OK
  OP->>UI: Type task + Dispatch
  UI->>BE: POST /api/build/{id}/dispatch
  BE->>LSQ: dispatch_wave(spec)
  LSQ->>RT: Runner::run(agent_spec)
  RT->>PROV: LlmAgentProvider::spawn
  PROV-->>RT: AgentResponse
  RT->>AYIN: span dispatch.agent
  RT-->>LSQ: AgentArtifact{path}
  LSQ-->>BE: WaveOutcome
  BE->>BE: write .tmp/dispatch-<id>/agent-*.md
  BE-->>UI: SSE event wave.complete
  UI->>UI: Switch to Results tab
  OP->>UI: Click artifact row
  UI->>BE: GET /api/dispatch/{id}/artifacts/agent-engineer.md
  BE-->>UI: file content
  UI->>UI: Render in Monaco read-only
